  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin-10mm-Step-1-1612374377464-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin-10mm-Step-1-1612374377464-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin-10mm-Step-1-1612374377464-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin-10mm-Step-1-1612374377464-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin-10mm-Step-1-1612374377464-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Empty-pan-1646666240578-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Empty-pan-1646666240578-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Empty-pan-1646666240578-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Empty-pan-1646666240578-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Empty-pan-1646666240578-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pan is hot, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>ground cumin </strong>and your <strong>ground coriander</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Chop your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646666292952-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646666292952-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646666292952-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646666292952-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1646666292952-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Drain and rinse your<strong> green lentils</strong></p><p>Once the spices are fragrant, add your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>spinach</strong> and <strong>half </strong>of<strong> </strong>your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chopped creamed coconut </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[350ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and give everything a good mix up and cook for 1 min further or until the spinach starts to wilt</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646666297096-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646666297096-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646666297096-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646666297096-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646666297096-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Ciabatta-in-toaster-1675789096952-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Ciabatta-in-toaster-1675789096952-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Ciabatta-in-toaster-1675789096952-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Ciabatta-in-toaster-1675789096952-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Ciabatta-in-toaster-1675789096952-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spinach starts to wilt, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>drained lentils </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>with a pinch of<strong> pepper</strong> and cook for a further 3-5 min or until thickened – this is your<strong> spiced lentil stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646666302479-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646666302479-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646666302479-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646666302479-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646666302479-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the stew is thickening, add your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>nigella seeds</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> chilli-peanut crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1646666305255-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1646666305255-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1646666305255-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1646666305255-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1646666305255-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> spiced lentil stew </strong>with the <strong>warmed ciabatta </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>chilli</strong>-<strong>peanut crumb</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
